node.text:
Happy Friday the 13th 💕🔪

May I present my blood, sweat and tears? The Little Ghost ‘21 Fall Collection; “Let’s Play”. 

For full access head to LittleGhostBootique.com

Let me know what you think in the comments, save the post, share, and help me spread the word as the ever-changing algorithm is hard for a small biz to beat 🥊 

💝 Monday/ I will pick one comment (Insta & Facebook page both eligible) to receive a loaded stash bag! (Includes; 1 Vinyl Stash Bag, 1 Silicone Hand Pipe, 1 Grinder, 1 Little Ghost Holographic Sticker, 1 Pair of Iridescent Ghost Earrings, a 3-pair Lash Book from @CannaBabeLashes)

💝 Within 24 hours/ I will pick one random Instagram story share of this post to receive a Trick ‘r Treat dab tool or roach clip + 1 pack of @YasQueenPapers (share your favorite piece to your story so I can see).

-Selected pr;ze w;nners must be 18+, and following both pr;ze sponsors @LittleGhostBootique & @CannaBabeLashes)

Thank you, thank you, thank you.

Enjoy! xo 🔪💕😶‍🌫️

🚨 I will never message anyone from a “new account” and redirect you to a site where you have to enter payment info to “claim a pr;ze”. If someone does create a fake account please report and block 💀

node.text:
I’ve been feeling the weight of being a one woman show lately. I’ve poured myself into the continued growth of Little Ghost, with big visions for the future and this Friday the 13th I’m launching my second ever full collection, while juggling the 30 other roles I play to keep this ship sailing. I am exhausted, but I am proud, beyond grateful and I am so thrilled with the direction Little Ghost is heading. I made this, but you all kept it alive. Every single order, your shares, and word of mouth referrals breathed life into my little dream. 

So please tune in tomorrow morning for the launch of 13 all new fall inspired menu pieces, a g!Veaway for 2, and some exciting shop news 💕

Thanks you for all the support along the way. Thank you for always keeping it weird 🎃🖤

📸 via @ninibee_
